<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1156</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>huō miǎn nián 迦南1156</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 chéng shú de pú táo lián chéng chuàn, jīn nián shì huō miǎn nián.
 shù shàng de guǒ zi xiāng yòu tián, jīn nián shì huō miǎn nián.
 yí luò de mài suì ér pù de miàn, jīn nián shì huō miǎn nián.
 chéng zhōng de dì xiōng lù chū xiào liǎn, jīn nián shì huō miǎn nián.
 huō miǎn nián nǎ huō miǎn nián, shén gěi tā de zi mín shī ēn de nián.
 huō miǎn nián nǎ huō miǎn nián, jiā jiā hù hù yǒu xiào liǎn.
 huō miǎn nián nǎ huō miǎn nián, shén de ér nǚ yào dà tuán yuán.
 huō miǎn nián nǎ huō miǎn nián, hǎo xìn xī yào chuán biàn.</lyrics>
</song>